scout_chillpillarena


This is a simple scout and knife map featuring a showdown of Counter-Terrorists and Terriorists at "The Tree of Knife". The objective for both teams is to eliminate the other team.

Map made during my days with the ChillPill-Club.com. See in-game signature plate for credits.

This map is a variant of ka_chillpillarena but was not released until Oct 2011. Nav place names and overview included.

---------------------------------


MAY 2011, ASTFA` (aka CenTor!oR`)
